skins.selfIntroduction: The Fletcher-class is pretty big, so it's not strange that you haven't heard of me. Though I had my fair share of dangerous moments, I managed to return peacefully. Right after that, I even went to live the Dragon Empery for a while! Is that why you think I look a bit bigger? Who knows~
skins.acquisition: Hello Commander, I am the Fletcher-class destroyer, Mullany. From today onwards, we'll be spending a lot of time together. Please take good care of me!
skins.login: Commander, have you eaten? Should I prepare something for you?
skins.details: Commander, please let me know if there's anything you need me for.
skins.secretaryIdle1: Aww... I thought I followed the recipe perfectly, so how did it turn out like this...?
skins.secretaryIdle2: Commander, make sure to strike the right balance between work and leisure! It's not good to be lazy or overworked~
skins.secretaryIdle3: Commander, do your best! Believe in yourself, you're the greatest!
skins.secretaryTouch: Uhh... the black smoke coming from that side of the kitchen? Ahaha... ha... I have no idea what you're talking about~
skins.secretarySpecialTouch: C-Commander... so you're also interested in the racy stuff...
skins.secretaryHeadpat: Being treated like a kid... feels a bit weird... ahaha...

skins.shipDescription: What's with the weird look, Commander? Ah, I got this outfit while studying abroad in the Dragon Empery. Umm... does it suit me?
skins.acquisition: What's with the weird look, Commander? Ah, I got this outfit while studying abroad in the Dragon Empery. Umm... does it suit me?
skins.login: Would you like to have some soup dumplings?
skins.details: After studying abroad in the Dragon Empery and being exposed to their history and culture, I've learned to be a bit calmer. However, I'm still the same person as before... as you can probably tell from my cooking...
skins.secretaryTouch: The elegance of ladies from the Empery, walking with their parasols opened, is a sight to behold. So, I picked up a few things from them - want to see?
skins.secretaryHeadpat: Commander, are you... interested in my new hairstyle?
